reviewText: Once Again This Was Nicole Oring Who Was Hot!

There is only one boy/girl scene and its ok.  There are 2 girl/girl scenes which are better.  Jenna Haze looks good in her shower scene.  There are also 2 girl masturbation scenes which are not bad.  What makes this different then the usual Torchlight video is that there is plenty of full frontal nudity in each scene.  Not great soft core but better then 80% of the torchlight videos.
